executor_description: This resource returns the route and directions between two or more points on a map. The directions can be either for walking or driving. The distance between two points and the estimate time of arrival is also provided.

This resource is used to return the number of ATM locations nearest to a given location. This allows an application to prepare the user interface or retrieve the amount of memory needed because there may be many results returned. For example, the requirements to show number of ATMs in a dense urban environment versus a rural area is quite different.
